    "body": "Problem:\r\nList items separated by blank lines are wrapped in \"blocks\", then the html generator does not treat them as contiguous list-items, and the browser shows the list as \"1. 1. 1.\" instead of \"1. 2. 3.\".\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\n- When generating a list-item, check if the last child of the previous   block was a list-item, and merge them together.\r\n- Massage the help source.\r\n\r\n\r\nfix #37220\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-22T01:13:27Z",
